videos.description: Miami guard Anthony Lawrence II delivers a bounce pass to Ebuka Izundu for a powerful dunk.
videos.headline: Izundu hammers home Miami's first points

videos.description: North Carolina runs the fast break and Cameron Johnson leaves a pass for Luke Maye, who rises up for a dunk and a foul.
videos.headline: Maye finishes and-1 slam in transition

videos.description: North Carolina freshman Coby White fights through the Miami defense for the hoop and the harm.
videos.headline: White powers through lane for and-1

videos.description: Miami Chris Lykes shows off his handles and drills a step-back 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Miami's Lykes nails step-back 3-pointer

videos.description: Miami's Chris Lykes nails a clutch 3-pointer to give the Hurricanes a late lead over North Carolina.
videos.headline: Lykes gives Miami lead with big 3

videos.description: Kenny Williams' 3-pointer gives UNC an overtime lead that the Tar Heels would not give up vs. Miami.
videos.headline: UNC's Williams hits 3-pointer for OT lead

videos.description: No. 8 North Carolina overcomes a late second-half deficit to defeat Miami in overtime 88-85.
